Privacy Policy for Jumpy Knight Game

Effective Date: 16.05.2023

This Privacy Policy outlines the practices and policies for the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use the Jumpy Knight game developed by Mazej Development. This policy applies to all users of the Game on any platform, including but not limited to Google Play. By using the Game, you agree to the collection and use of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information: We do not collect personally identifiable information, such as your name, address, email address, or phone number, unless you voluntarily provide it to us for support or feedback purposes.

1.2 Non-Personal Information: When you use the Game, we may collect non-personal information, including but not limited to device information, technical information about your usage, and anonymous analytics data. This information helps us improve the Game and provide a better user experience.

Use of Information
2.1 Personal Information: Any personally identifiable information you provide to us will only be used to respond to your inquiries or feedback and improve our services. We will not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties without your consent unless required by law.

2.2 Non-Personal Information: We may use non-personal information for various purposes, including but not limited to analyzing usage patterns, improving the Game's performance, and enhancing user experience. This information may be aggregated and anonymized to ensure your privacy is protected.

Third-Party Services
3.1 Advertising: The Game may include third-party advertisements. These ad networks may collect non-personal information about your interaction with the advertisements. Please review the privacy policies of these third-party ad networks for more information on their practices and how to opt-out.

3.2 Analytics: We may use third-party analytics tools to gather non-personal information about your use of the Game. These tools help us understand user behavior and improve the Game's features and performance. The information collected by these analytics providers is subject to their own privacy policies.

Data Security
We are committed to protecting the security of your personal information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your information, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Children's Privacy
The Game is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have inadvertently collected personal information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately, and we will take reasonable steps to delete it.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes we make will be posted on this page, and the revised version will be effective immediately upon posting. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, please contact us at [Your contact email].

By using the Flappy Falcon Game, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
